v0.1.0 (2014-06-29)
-------------------

* Implemented settings to modify the behavior of the patching proess.
* Refactored the class ``ExtensionSet`` towards using an ``add()`` method.
* Cleaned-up the ``Extension.__init__()`` method from the parameters not required to construct the class.
* Got the ``ExtensionsRegistrar.register_extensions()`` function to return a single ``ExtensionSet`` object.
* Added a FAQ section to the doc.
* Minor tweaks to the code.
* Minor tweaks to the doc.


